    "This collaborative nature of software development presents unique challenges and opportunities for decentralized program repair techniques.",
    "Addressing the Gap.",
    "We focus on LLM-based program repair with a decentralized setting to explore the potential of collaborative learning while preserving data privacy.",
    "We simulate a number of distributed devices and datasets in the federated learning system to investigate the practicality of federated fine-tuning and provide insights that may benefit further research for decentralized program repair or other code-related tasks.",
